org.livingdoc.api

Annotation Type Before


  • @Target
 @Retention
public Before

    Methods annotated with this annotation are invoked before the first fixture of an annotationclass ExecutableDocument or before the first scenario annotationclass Step method is invoked.

    Constraints:

    1. The annotated method must not have any parameters!
    2. If multiple methods of a single fixture are annotated the invocation order is non-deterministic!

    See Also:
    annotationclass ExecutableDocument, annotationclass Step, annotationclass ExecutableDocument, annotationclass Step, annotationclass ScenarioFixture
